---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About — Zahiruddin Tavargere" description="Senior GenAI Architect at Dell, YouTuber, and community builder.">
  <div class="container">
    <section class="about-page">
      <h1>Zahiruddin Tavargere</h1>
      <p class="sub">Senior Principal Engineer & GenAI Architect @ Dell · Bengaluru, India</p>

      <div class="prose">
        <h2>Background</h2>
        <p>I'm a firm believer in social learning. I owe my dev career to all the tech content creators I learned from — this site is my contribution back to the community.</p>
        <p>After 15+ years building distributed systems, automation tools, and software architecture, I was tasked to lead a GenAI team at Dell. I transitioned into AI engineering within 3 months and have been deep in the agent-building world ever since.</p>

        <h2>At Dell</h2>
        <p>Senior Principal Engineer & Generative AI Architect, building AI Acceleration Platform solutions. AI Hackathon winner (2017), Quality Hackout (2018), Cloud IT Hackathon (2016).</p>

        <h2>Why this site</h2>
        <p>There is a lot of AI content out there. Most of it is surface-level or written by people who haven't shipped real agents. Everything here is grounded in actual implementation experience and honest learnings.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="links">
        <p class="section-label">Find me elsewhere</p>
        <a href="https://youtube.com/@adaptiveengineer" target="_blank">YouTube — Adaptive Engineer ↗</a>
        <a href="https://newsletter.adaptiveengineer.com" target="_blank">Newsletter — The Adaptive Engineer ↗</a>
        <a href="https://zahere.com" target="_blank">Blog — zahere.com ↗</a>
        <a href="https://twitter.com/zahiruddin_t" target="_blank">Twitter — @zahiruddin_t ↗</a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/zahiruddin-tavargere" target="_blank">LinkedIn ↗</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-page { max-width: 600px; padding: 4rem 0 5rem; }
  h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin-bottom: 0.35rem; }
  .sub { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 3rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 2rem; }
  .links { margin-top: 3rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
  .section-label { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .links a { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--muted); width: fit-content; transition: color 0.15s; }
  .links a:hover { color: var(--text); }
</style>
